<HEAD>Mother Kills Child, Self</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HAYWARD, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A mother stabbed her 4-year-old daughter
to death and then fatally turned the knife on herself as her
2-year-old son hid in a rear bedroom of their apartment, according
to police.
   Laverne Romero, 20, was pronounced dead Thursday night at Eden
Hospital Medical Center in Castro Valley from multiple stab wounds
to the chest and abdomen. The girl, Veronica Ponce, died in surgery.
   Romero's son, Felipe Ponce, was unharmed, said Sgt. Thomas West.
The boy will be placed in protective custody, police said.
