that Romero used at least three knives from the kitchen set.
   He said Romero, a single parent, ``was emotionally upset over
something'' and apparently stabbed the child several times before
she stabbed herself.
   Edward Ortega, a neighbor, said he could hear the girl scream:
``No, Mommy. Help, Mommy.''
