<HEAD>Bright Lights, Big Wedding? Michael J. Fox and Former Co-Star to
Marry</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Michael J. Fox, star of NBC's ``Family
Ties,'' is planning to marry actress Tracy Pollan, his former
girlfriend on the show, the actor's agent said Friday.
   Fox's agent, Peter Benedek, said through an assistant only that
the actor was getting married but wouldn't say where or when.
   However, a source close to the actor said Fox would ``be married
