   Eighteen young women from regions across the state will be
competing Saturday for the title of Miss New York State. The
judging is based 50 percent on talent and 50 percent on a combined
personal interview, evening gown and swimsuit competition.
   Miss New York will receive $3,500 toward college expenses and a
berth in the Miss America contest in September.
